          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Son of Man,"
            },
            {
              "chord": "Em7",
              "text": "Pioneer,"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "He has"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "led the"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "way;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Following, how we sing, Jesus leads us"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "on;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "Em",
              "text": "We are"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "marching"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "with the"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "Victor"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "to"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "the"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "throne."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "On we go, on we go to the throne with Him;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "On we go through this age, age so dark and grim;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then shall we—formerly, Satan’s captured ones—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be exalted with the Lord upon His throne."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Called as sons, called as sons, destined to be kings;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Called as sons we’ve no time for the worldly things:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet we know, it is so—we don’t qualify!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus the Lord must search and burn and purify."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Search and burn, search and burn all our inward parts;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Search and burn, thoroughly, to refine our hearts;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll not fear, but be clear—burning, searching thus"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is the gracious visit of the Lord to us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With the Man, with the Man is a rainbow fair;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Glorious bow, ’round the throne, faithfulness declares:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We deserved to be served with God’s judgment sore,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But we have been spared to praise Him more and more."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
  ],
